casebody.data:
No. 10-5946. Barbara Robinson, Petitioner v. Eric H. Holder, Jr., Attorney General. 562 U.S. 824, 131 S. Ct. 387,

178 L. Ed. 2d 21,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 6287. October 4, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner is allowed until October 25, 2010, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to *22submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
